message.content: A web site is a collection of related web pages, which are accessed through a common URL or domain name. It is typically hosted on a server and designed for public access. A web site can contain a variety of multimedia content including text, images, audio, and video. The visual characteristics of a web site can vary widely, but typically include a consistent layout, typography, color scheme, and imagery that reflect the brand or purpose of the site. A web site is often used as a platform for generating leads, providing information, or selling products or services. It can be accessed through a range of devices, including desktop and mobile devices, and is commonly found through search engines, social media, or direct URL input.
